  "riddle": "1. Unearth the political path of Brijendra Pratap Singh, tracing his allegiance to which party does he belong?\n\n2. What governing body in Madhya Pradesh features a duo of leaders assisting its chief?\n\n3. In the election that reshaped the assembly's landscape, how many seats did the Indian National Congress capture?\n\n4. Ascend to new heights; what is the elevation (in meters) of the capital where this electoral contest took place?\n\n5. Scour the vicinity of the previous electoral event: how many dining establishments tempt the hungry travelers nearby?\n\n6. Using the elevation from clue 4 and the nearby restaurant count from clue 5, compute the absolute difference between these two values.\n\n7. Revisit the heights of the location discussed in clue 4; what elevation in meters does it boast?\n\n8. Flip the numerals of the seat count won in clue 3; what integer emerges when you reverse its digits?\n\n9. Calculate the digital root of the total obtained from adding the values revealed in clues 3 and 7 together. Conclusively, this will yield a single digit that holds a key to your quest.",
